Woman dumped her husband’s body in a pit and poured concrete near Belgorod
In the Belgorod region, the woman confessed to the murder of her husband, whom she threw into a pit with waste and poured concrete, according to the website of the regional administration of the IC of the Russian Federation.
It is noted that the suspect lived in a marriage with the murdered since 1999.
In recent years, the husband began to abuse alcohol and after another quarrel, the woman decided to murder.
“When the husband fell asleep, the suspect tied his hands and feet, put a plastic bag on his head and pressed a pillow.
When the husband stopped showing signs of life, she wrapped the body in a carpet, carried it out into the yard and hid it in the cesspool.
The next day, she called a concrete mixer and poured concrete into the pit,” the department said.
The woman later reported that her husband was missing.
Relatives of the deceased turned to the police, who opened the hole and retrieved the body.
The investigation intends to ask the court for the arrest of the suspect.
The criminal investigation is currently ongoing.
